summary:
Villanelle.
She is a player. She plays out her life as if in a comedy where the audience laughs behind the scenes. And most...
body:
💐

Villanelle.

She is a player. She plays out her life as if in a comedy where the audience laughs behind the scenes. And most importantly - she can afford it.

Interesting is she afraid to die? She clings to life, but I think that this is only because she will be wondering what will happen next.

I do not like such heroes (villains without motivation), but it’s interesting, isn’t it?

title: Payback
description:
by allingoodtime

When your life no longer means anything to you because the love of your life has been taken from you. A person can change and become something they never wanted to be. A person who seeks revenge from an insane woman who goes out her way to destroy Claire Fraser life. And it all started with fan fiction Claire Fraser wrote one day after recovering from a great loss—a loss of child. Claire had started a blog on tumblr and joined a fan fiction community on A03. Writing fan fiction had been Claire’s way of escaping her grief from losing a child. But, what she did not realize…Was that, there are those who stalk the internet for victims. Most of the time it’s for stealing money, but there are those who stalk people because their sick minds think there is nothing wrong with hacking into someones computer stalking and stealing from them. Claire would be one of those victims and so would her husband, Jamies Fraser. Here begins a story that some of you might know from experience and others hope will never happen to them. But, don’t think it won’t happen to you. Never say never. That’s what Claire Fraser use to say until Villanelle decided Claire’s life was her for the taken.
